        "subject": "LU-8262 lbuid: use mytget to download source RPMs",
        "message": "LU-8262 lbuid: use mytget to download source RPMs\n\nWhen Internet connection is not good enough, wget or curl is not\nquick or robust enough when downloading source RPMs. Mytget is a\nmulti-thread download tool which could improve this situation\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I44c79f97b9300ffe7f82e15915a937756a1690fc"
